query.name: Query A
query.query: select count(distinct vid) as uniqueVcount, osm_id from trajectory_paths group by osm_id order by uniqueVcount desc limit 100
query.info: This is the info for query A

query.name: Query B
query.query: select count(*) as count, osm_id from trajectory_paths group by osm_id order by count desc limit 100
query.info: This is the info for query B

query.name: Query ERROR
query.query: select count(*) as cot, osm_id from trajectpaths group by osm_id or0
